    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel token from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The process of issuing tokens to the people standing in line will be started from today (27) in order to advance the limited fuel reserve distribution.",
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekera has said that people standing in line at petrol stations will be given tokens made by the three forces.",
        "Meanwhile, two government ministers are scheduled to visit Russia today to discuss fuel imports from Russia."
      ],
